%% 3.2.16 Verify Top-up Status — sequence
%% GET /api/Wallet/GetPayOsTopUpStatus/{orderCode} polling
%% POST /api/Wallet/HandlePayOsWebhook — PayOS calls backend (parallel)
%% BR69: Verify PayOS signature before crediting wallet

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant WC as WalletController
    participant WS as WalletService
    participant PayOS as PayOS
    participant DB as SQL Server

    par App polling
        loop Until success or timeout
            App->>WC: GET /api/Wallet/GetPayOsTopUpStatus/{orderCode}
            WC->>WS: GetPayOsTopUpStatusAsync
            WS->>DB: READ payment state
            WC-->>App: status
        end
    and Webhook
        PayOS->>WC: POST /api/Wallet/HandlePayOsWebhook
        WC->>WS: HandlePayOsWebhookAsync — verify signature (BR69)
        WS->>DB: Credit wallet + log
    end

    App->>Guardian: Top-up successful — updated balance
